%N A396022 Decimal expansion of (2+sqrt(2))/(2*Pi).
%C A396022 The probability that Buffon’s needle (see A060294), bent at its midpoint at a 90 degrees angle, will land on a line when dropped onto a floor with parallel lines spaced at a distance equal to the length of the needle.
%H A396022 Uwe Bäsel, <a href="https://doi.org/10.5169/seals-630622">Buffon's problem with a pivot needle</a>, Elemente der Mathematik, Vol. 70, No. 2 (2015), pp. 67-70. See Remark 1, p. 70.
